plot: The film is based on a true yet unsolved murder case from the early 1990s that is known among Koreans as the &"disappearance of the frog children.&" In 1991, five elementary school students told their parents that they were going to hang out on a nearby mountain to catch frogs. They never came back.   Written by  Stanislav S, Sochi, Russia
title: Children (2011)
